Package: multisynthdid
Type: Package
Title: Multiple outcome Synthetic Difference-in-Differences
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Agoston", "Reguly", , "agoston.reguly@uni-corvinus.hu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8615-3192"))
Maintainer: Agoston Reguly <agoston.reguly@uni-corvinus.hu>
Description: Allows to use multiple outcomes in Synthetic Diff-in-Diffs estimation. The package extends Arkhangelsky et al (2021) to multiple outcomes, while optimizing the weights over multiple variables.
